show.description: For three long years, Ellie Scott awaited a heart transplant for her son, Howie. However, her husband, Dr. Zack Scott, shattered her hopes by giving the heart to his ex-lover Rachel Shields' son, Jason. Devastated by Howie’s death, Ellie confronted Zack, who blamed her and moved Rachel and Jason into their home. Ellie demanded a divorce, but Zack refused. In desperation, Ellie caused a scene at the hospital, leading to Zack's suspension and Rachel's dismissal. Realizing his grave mistake, Zack was consumed with regret. Ellie forced Rachel to face Howie's portrait, exposing her deceit. In a final act of redemption, Zack sacrificed his life to save Ellie, and Rachel was imprisoned.
